*	 While this course is meant to view singing as a method of expression on stage, the individual and group practices will be aimed to train the students' individual vocal skills according to the methodology of acting. The course will also help future actors to transition from speech to song on stage and to combine singing and dancing, as it is necessary for operettas and musicals.Learning outcomes/õpiväljund:  By the end of the course, the student will have: *	Better individual vocal abilities, a better sense of rhythm and ensemble, according to their own expectations and past experiences *	New experience in the field of solo- and group singing *	The basics of transitioning from speech to song and vice versa on stage *	The basics of combining song and dance on stage
